entries.femaleVariant: <kiroshi l="creo" o="Ou te bloke la a pandan prèske karant èdtan." t="You were stuck in there for almost forty hours." b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Okenn sekirite, Okenn bakòp. Mwen pa sezi ki ou ..." t="No security, no backup. No surprise that you..." b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Si m mande anraje?" t="That I went crazy?" b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Ou te tande kèk bagay dròl. Ou te dezidrate epi lòlòj tap vire tout boulin." t="That you heard some weird things. You were dehydrated and overclocked." b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Se sa manzè te di m. Si mwen te ka rete pi lontan." t="That's what she told me. If I could stay longer." b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Kiyès ki di w sa?" t="Who told you?" b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Se pa enpòtan." t="Doesn't matter." b="" a=""/>
